Popular dancehall singer Shavey famed for the hit song Gyal has passed away. The news on his passing was first posted by Grandpa Records and later Ulopa the producer behind their hit song confirmed the same on his social media account. Witness accounts report that Shavey was run over by a matatu plying the Kayole Route and celebrities have been busy condoling with his family and fans through messages posted. “Gone way way too soon….. A brother, family, no words are ever enough… Life is too short. Rest in peace shavey de king of de riddim!!!!” posted Ulopa.